zm_MkZk_Proto_XS_v1

Extra small version of zm_MkZk_Proto

  • Spawns are outside, objective is to get into the house and defend your section of choice.
  • 15 seconds after reaching the entrance area the frontdoor can be locked.
  • Most doors and windows are barricaded with destructable woodplanks.
  • Surveilance-system based in the attic to watch outside-areas around the house.

If there are things to fix or ideas for improvement let me know!
